Package com.example.eventplanner

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.example.eventplanner.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.os.Parcelable
public class User extends Object implements android.os.Parcelable
User class represents a user in the application. It contains user information such as name, homepage, contact information, profile picture, and various lists related to events.
